{"tid":17016,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHK需要創造一個共治平台","createTime":"2016-12-01T16:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T19:18:16.000Z","uid":14197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2277d5266cde6a9f66d73050e7ce376d7ae429fe","tid":17016,"uid":14197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:07:20.000Z","msg":"見到剛剛admin公開被bam名單，呢個係一個德政<br />\n<br />\n增加透明度，往往係人民既渴求<br />\n<br />\n眼見既然而家個論壇有好多野都未設置好，有好多野都未有一個明確嘅政策實行或者有一個比較好嘅指引。<br />\n<br />\n制度建立需時，倒不如開放比公眾參與同諮詢，巴絲可以比多d意見<br />\n<br />\n依家仲有好多需要優化嘅制度，我哋絕對要摒棄舊高登做得唔好嘅地方，採納一個新嘅方式，憂人民所憂，咁樣LIHK先至會建立得穩固，成為真正屬於我哋嘅平台<br />\n<br />\n以下我提出小小建議，大家公開討論，亦都需要大家加插不同嘅政策<br />\n<br />\n1. emoji 存在性<br />\n2. 公開被bam 名單及原因<br />\n3. app既功能優化，例如增加反pm<br />\n3. pm功能增加<br />\n4. 增加isp既email 嘅選項，好多大專院校都登記唔到<br />\n5. 網頁版嘅設計？<br />\n6.增加或者減少某幾個台？<br />\n<br />\n我先少少拋磚引玉，大家再補充"},{"pid":"7150deab2080450a70b1d4a394fc47751b84d31b","tid":17016,"uid":26176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:09:06.000Z","msg":"你係咪有補充障礙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2d43396f8d9f942f8fceaaa0723e09417473e8","tid":17016,"uid":14197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪有補充障礙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acd9bb0f41c2e6341802997cc965f3d03e8c142","tid":17016,"uid":14197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:43:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82c49d6ff6feccd0af26547a05f3faa820b5430c","tid":17016,"uid":14197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/014606_eb09782d34d87d771a69799c290ffa3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F014606